msgid "Apply Aria attributes to the mobile (burger) menu to make it accessible."
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-divi-accessibility-admin.php:381
msgid "Fix duplicate menu ids"
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-divi-accessibility-admin.php:388
msgid ""
"Because Divi uses the same menu twice (Once for the primary menu and again "
"for the mobile menu), the unique ID's are duplicated causing validation "
"issues. This option prevents WordPress from adding a unique ID to the menu "
"list items."
msgstr ""

